bilingual.source: Just because the hellbender isn't big like an elephant or beautiful like a tiger doesn't mean it doesn't deserve that.
bilingual.target: 仅仅因为大鲵不像大象那样大或像老虎那样美丽，并不意味着它不值得拥有这一席之地。

bilingual.source: Your dress is beautiful, you deserve all the compliments.
bilingual.target: 你的裙子很漂亮，你值得所有的赞美。

bilingual.source: She misplaced her trust in someone who didn't deserve it.
bilingual.target: 她放错地方了信任，信任了不值得信任的人。

bilingual.source: The frontline workers deserve our utmost respect and support.
bilingual.target: 前线工作人员值得我们最大的尊重和支持。

bilingual.source: Do not mistreat animals; they deserve our care and respect.
bilingual.target: 不要虐待动物，它们值得我们的关爱和尊重。

bilingual.source: The front-line workers deserve our utmost respect and support.
bilingual.target: 前线工作人员值得我们最大的尊重和支持。
他们确实值得这样的享受。

bilingual.source: In fact, they need and deserve to be cared for.
bilingual.target: 事实上，他们需要并且值得被照顾。

bilingual.source: I wish you happiness, you deserve it.

list.abstract: Your suggestion deserves to be considered.
deserve是由吴亦凡演唱的英文单曲，于北京时间2017年10月12日零点，在Spotify、iTunes两大平台全球（大陆地区除外）上线。

yingyinNormal.en: And we all deserve a standing ovation at least once in our lives. My friends do. My teachers do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个人都值得大家站起来为他鼓掌一次。我的朋友们值得。我的老师们值得。

yingyinNormal.en: No, someone doesn't treat you the way you deserve, then they don't deserve to have you. My dad always told that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不会 如果一个人不好好以你值得拥有的方式对待你，他们也就不配得到你，我爸爸总那么跟我说。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my God, you know, maybe you're right. Maybe I don't need him. I deserve to be treated with respect.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天哪，也许你是对的，可能我并不需要他。我值得尊重。

yingyinNormal.en: Bert, you're a good guy; you deserve a woman who's interested in more than just your money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 伯特，你是个好人；你值得被一个爱你而不是只爱你的钱的女人爱。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, Farkle. Where is she? Whatever have I done to deserve this display of affection?
yingyinNormal.zh: 法尔科，她人哪儿去了？我这是做了什么值得你在大庭广众之下表达爱意？

yingyinNormal.en: I got one. Socks. Because your family's feet deserve the best. Honey, leave it to the pros.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想到一个，“袜子，因为你家人的脚值得用最好的”。亲爱的，让专业的人说好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Bec. Seven, fine, but only because there are three of them. Baby, And the thing is, I'm trying really hard to get us to a nine. Because they are cute kids, and they deserve nine parents.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小贝……那就七分，但那只是因为我们有三个孩子。宝贝……问题是我拼命想达到九分的标准，因为这些可爱的孩子值得九分的父母。

yingyinNormal.en: The American people deserve to know, anyway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国人民反正也该知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Better than I deserve, most likely. And you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 比我应得的还要好。你呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Pregnant workers deserve to be treated fairly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怀孕的员工应该得到公平地对待。

yingyinNormal.en: New parents deserve quality, affordable childcare.
yingyinNormal.zh: 刚刚做父母的人应该得到高质量，可负担的婴儿保育项目。

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs Hughes, doesn't Carson deserve a wedding in this house?
yingyinNormal.zh: 休斯太太，卡森难道不该在这里办婚礼吗？

yingyinNormal.en: They deserve it? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们是咎由自取? 没错。

yingyinNormal.en: Shame on you, Arthur! You don't deserve your crown, and you don't deserve your queen!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你配不上王冠，也配不上王后！
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: I want to be taken seriously. I deserve a later curfew.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想得到你们的严肃对待，我应该可以晚点回家。

yingyinNormal.en: But such a sacrifice must be earned. We must deserve it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但必须让他的这种牺牲有意义，要让他死的其所。

yingyinNormal.en: Two of the victims are in this court. They deserve an answer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天有两位受害人在场。她们应该得到答案。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Hey. Look, I understand if you came by to hit me, I deserve it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你是来打我的，我了解，这是我活该。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll take you in without breaking you. Which is more than you deserve.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会在不打烂你的前提下送你进监狱，你应该感恩戴德。

yingyinNormal.en: If I'm gonna lock up this nomination for you, I deserve to be compensated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要是帮你拿下了提名，我应该得到报酬。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: do something or have or show qualities worthy of reward or punishment

examination_example.sentence_trans: 职业统计学家应该得到更多的尊重。

examination_example.sentence: "The Heart of the Matter," the just-released report by the American Academy of Arts and Sciences (AAAS), <highlight>deserves</highlight> praise .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国艺术与科学学院刚刚发布的报告《问题的核心》值得称赞。

examination_example.sentence: Ensure that only the most <highlight>deserving</highlight> claimants received their benefits.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 确保只有最有资格的申请人才能得到他们的利益。
